column5: Date: Saturday, June 27, 2009  Time: 9:00am - 1:00pm  Location: Northport Park  Lots of prizes and trophies for the kids including the "Big Fish" of the day prize, a Quantum Controller spinning combo donated by Ron at Skevy's Outdoor Specialities.  Fishing starts at 9:00am and ends at 11:00 am with tophies , prizes and BBQ to follow  2 dollars per child ages 4-12  Worms provided but bring your own fishing gear and floatation device if wanted
